                                grades</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Webinars</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col">
                    <h5>Platform</h5>
                    <ul class="nav flex-column">
                        <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-secondary">Parterners
